  "description": "<i>Colony</i> is a scrolling <a id=\"d69727e0b86eb95c662ad65907ec0beb2\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=missile+command\"> Missile Command</a> clone. As in Missile Command the aim of the game is to protect bases (you have six of them) from incoming missiles. Beside ordinary missiles, blue and red multi-missiles will be fired at your bases by bombers and attack satellites. After every fifth level you are awarded with an extra base and as in missile command the game is lost when all your bases has been destroyed. The game is controlled by the joystick.\n",
